                    |Vacation Quest: The Hawaiian Islands v1.0.0.0|
                    +---------------------------------------------+

+----------------+
|Game Description|
+----------------+

Discover your passport to the world's most exotic locations! Relax in the tropics as you search for hidden clues to extend your vacation and unlock new adventures. Explore 28 island scenes in search of over 2,300 hidden objects. Find the seashells in each location to earn bonus days and tour new sites. Fill your vacation journal with achievements and go for a Perfect Search to boost your score! Kick back in untimed Vacation mode or compete against the clock. It's your own tropical paradise!

Originally released November 18th, 2010.

+----------------------------------+
|Instructions / System Requirements|
+----------------------------------+

No install or crack is required for this portable version. Extract the ZIP file and create a shortcut to the executable (EXE) to play.

This game is compatible with Windows 2000, XP, Vista(32/64bit) and 7(32/64bit). Requires DirectX 7.0 or later. Processor requirements: 350MHz CPU or higher. RAM requirements: 128 MB or higher. Requires a DirectX-compatible Sound and Video card with at least 16 MB of video memory.

